title: Pixel 1 to Pixel 4a 5g - will website shortcut folders copy across during the data transfer process?
content: I have read the set up process and cannot find an answer to this.... I'm sure like most people I have multiple folders set up for my needs and having to recreate them I seriously considering if it's worth upgrading. Thanks in advance.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device, Google Pixel 4a (5G)
